These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Movie-Genre: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
Flower: rose, orchid, amaryllis, marigold
1. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the left of Movie-Genre:crime##1
2. Movie-Genre:crime is on the right of Movie-Genre:thriller##1
3. Flower:orchid is on the far left or far right##3
4. Movie-Genre:musical is on the right of Flower:amaryllis##1
5. Flower:marigold is between Flower:orchid and Flower:amaryllis##2
6. Movie-Genre:thriller == Flower:rose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Flower     | rose     | amaryllis | marigold  | orchid      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, berlin, paris
Transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. City:san-francisco is on the left of Transport:helicopter##1
2. Transport:trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. City:paris is on the left of Transport:trike##1
4. Transport:trike is on the right of Transport:helicopter##1
5. City:berlin is on the far right##1
6. Transport:bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| City   | hannover | san-francisco    | paris     | berlin  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

