.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
City: hannover, london, new-york, boston
1. City:london is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
3. City:hannover is on the left or right of City:london##3
4. Beverage:fanta is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
5. City:boston == Beverage:soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| City      | london | hannover | new-york       | boston |

